            "body": "The `.response` attribute should be an empty list nowadays and not `None`. Despite that it's also irrelevant for this issue, as the web server should only care about the iterator returned when flask calls the response object with the environ and start_response function.\n\nGiven that there has been no activity on this issue for almost 4 years, I'm closing this until someone can reproduce it.\n"
